{
  "stem": "7860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You know everything what's going on around you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there's a man with a bottle of whiskey in his hand dressed like a Jew, Orthodox Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could imagine, an Orthodox Jew on a railroad station in Warsaw, in the middle of the war, drunk as drunk could be, singing songs, and dressed like a Hasidic Jew?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the Poles over there on the station round him up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the way, there was a Klezmer band, they would call it, Capella.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was playing music to entertain the people over there, while on the train-- on the station, because they had many professional entertainers that used to pass the hat around.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this drunken Jew, supposedly Jew, dancing to the music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the Poles were pushing him back and forth like throwing a ball back and forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And before I realized, whistles start blowing, and Germans surrounded the whole bunch of them, and hauled them all off on trucks to forced labor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shot some of them who tried to make an escape on the station in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another incident happened, I remember, where I was working in Garwolin-- which was my favorite little town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The station was a little bit away from town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were Germans unloading hay for the horses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were Jews unloading for them for the German army, the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Jews were eating the same as the German soldiers, soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was lunch time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the field kitchen they had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't tell the Jews who I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they gave me a bowl of soup, and I was eating the soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A Jewish man gave it to me without telling him that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one of the soldiers went to relieve himself in a hay stack.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
